- I was thinking the same about you.
- I'm just gonna say one word.

1169
01:20:21,629 --> 01:20:24,149
- "Midway."
- Oh, what a night!

1170
01:20:24,229 --> 01:20:26,509
We got hit midships
by a torpedo.

1171
01:20:26,589 --> 01:20:28,629
Just then a Japanese zero
comes in real low.

1172
01:20:28,709 --> 01:20:31,109
I get him in my sights,
flames all around.

1173
01:20:31,189 --> 01:20:35,149
Gun's so hot I can hardly handle it.
Rat-tat-tat, rat-tat-tat.

1174
01:20:35,229 --> 01:20:38,109
I get him! Take that,
you motherless son of Hirohito!

1175
01:20:38,189 --> 01:20:40,029
Then we spot
another one!

1176
01:20:40,109 --> 01:20:43,830
- We weren't attacked by zeroes!
- You calling me a liar?

1177
01:20:43,909 --> 01:20:47,069
- Oh no.
- Son, I think you should talk to Gwen.

1178
01:20:47,110 --> 01:20:49,389
- Whose side were you on?
- I can't now.

1179
01:20:49,429 --> 01:20:52,229
- It's important you talk to her.
- Who won the '43 world series?

1180
01:20:52,309 --> 01:20:53,749
- Bernie. Pop!
- Newton!

1181
01:20:53,830 --> 01:20:56,229
- Daddy!
- Gwen!

1182
01:21:04,670 --> 01:21:07,309
Winston, hi.
That's not what happened at all.

1183
01:21:07,389 --> 01:21:09,269
- It isn't?
- No. I mean...

1184
01:21:09,309 --> 01:21:13,229
Dad went through quite a lot during...
you know, the big one.

1185
01:21:13,310 --> 01:21:16,149
Iwo?

1186
01:21:16,229 --> 01:21:18,110
Happened to
a lot of good men.

1187
01:21:18,189 --> 01:21:19,909
Yeah!

1188
01:21:19,989 --> 01:21:22,189
- I wanted to show you...
- So beautiful!

1189
01:21:22,269 --> 01:21:25,829
- Uh-huh. - Davis, would you
sing "Too-ra-loo-ra-loo-ral"?

1190
01:21:25,909 --> 01:21:28,029
- What?
- This would be the perfect time.

1191
01:21:28,109 --> 01:21:32,669
I was so moved by that story when you
brought tears to your father's eyes.

1192
01:21:32,749 --> 01:21:36,829
- No, no, no.
- It would mean a great deal to me.

1193
01:21:43,229 --> 01:21:46,709
Davis has consented
to sing a song...

1194
01:21:46,790 --> 01:21:49,149
which is very special
to him and his dad.

1195
01:21:49,229 --> 01:21:52,149
Come on, sing.

